textBeforeTable: I have some leads on Gunshot and Pelli Chesukundam, and Kannadastore says that they have Mitheleya Seetheyaru and Janani. And my monthly searching for titles turned up Subhash on youtube, so I have hope that more titles will appear in random ways. UPDATE 6/22/12:  Thanks! If you are able to help me track down any of these films, I will happily pay the costs of acquisition and shipping. Any format--dvd, vcd, vhs, file--is fine. You will have my eternal gratitude, plus I’ll happily return the favor of tracking down mysterious items for you. Please feel free to post any leads or suggestions in the comments, or email me at dustdevil dot liz at gmail dot com. (For some of the films, I have found songs and short clips. These are definitely helpful, but my ultimate goal is to find the full movie.) the illegal trade in Soundarya-Jagapati Babu films of the early 2000's available in the usual places, but in a different language version (Hindi dub of Telugu, Telugu dub of Kannada, etc.) in a mysterious corner of the internet (youtube, dailymotion, etc), discovered by someone with superior google-skills on television, in the middle of the night in the bargain bin at a local dvd shop I’m posting this in the hope that more eyes looking for these films will yield results.  I’ll update and post this
